race.comment: EL FORTRESS (1) is back after a break of four months. Went close to a maiden win before the layoff, finishing second at his latest appearance over 1200m at Rockhampton. Placed in a recent trial and looks the one to beat. SHOOTINGOFFTHEHAND (3) resumed from a spell last start with a sound second over 1100m at this track. Placed to advantage and can take this out. BETTER BREAKOUT (2) finished third over 1100m at Scone at his most recent appearance on June 23. Lines up today for trainer Joanna Hassett. Has found the right race and is worth including. OSCAR BODIE (6) will be rock-hard fit for this and may earn some minor money.
